    Synopsis: Come to Call

    Go read Dumas' Count of Monte Cristo. Then listen to Nine Inch Nails' The Becoming about 1,000 times. Then think about how much of our national debt is owned by China. Then punch yourself in the junk. A lot. With brass knuckles. And ... THERE! That's about it. Can't wait to read it, right?
